### config file

## Add author
## Default: Computer user name

author=$(whoami)

## Change default text editor
## Default: System default (or nano if none is set)
## Uncomment or write your preferred editor to change

text_editor="${EDITOR:-nano}"
#text_editor="vim"
#text_editor="emacs"

## Default path for program files
## Move the .plog folder and change the path here if you want to locate the program folder elsewhere
program_folder="/home/$USER/.plog"

# Enables warning message before editing
# change it to "off" to turn off the warning
edit_warning="off"

# Might add settings for auto backup, case sensitive search and entry title
